description.original: A plugin to help you plan your day and setup pomodoro timers; fork of the original plugin by James Lynch (which stopped at 0.5.8) which preserves the look/feel and behavior of the original.
description.translation: A plugin to help you plan your day and setup pomodoro timers; fork of the original plugin by James Lynch (which stopped at 0.5.8) which preserves the look/feel and behavior of the original.
